'''紀淡海峽'''（{{jpn|j=紀淡海峡|hg=きたんかいきょう|rm=Kitan kaikyō|f=y}}）是一個位於[[日本|日本]][[和歌山縣|和歌山縣]]與[[淡路島|淡路島]]之間的[[海峽|海峽]]。該海峽總長約11公里，海峽中央有座名為[[友島|友島]]的沉水[[大陸島|大陸島]]，該島大幅減少建造跨海大橋所需的成本。<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=3tGWLabecNwC&pg=PA66&hl=zh-CN|publisher={{link-en|WIT Press|WIT Press}}|date=2011|isbn=978-1-84564-056-9|language=en|first=J. A.|last=Jurado|first2=José Ángel Jurado|last2=Albarracín|title=Bridge Aeroelasticity: Sensitivity Analysis and Optimal Design|pages=66}}</ref><!--Interesting claim re Awaji - how reliable is this source?--><ref>{{Cite book|url=http://www.crcnetbase.com/doi/book/10.1201/NOE9058096043|publisher=[[泰勒-弗朗西斯|Taylor & Francis]]|date=2003-01|isbn=978-90-5809-604-3|doi=10.1201/noe9058096043.ch173|language=en|editor-first=H|editor-last=Di Benedetto|title=Deformation Characteristics of Geomaterials / Comportement Des Sols Et Des Roches Tendres|pages=1363ff|chapter=Chapter 173: Compression characteristics of stiff clay to support a bridge foundation evaluated by field and laboratory tests}}</ref>該海峽全境位於[[瀨戶內海國立公園|瀨戶內海國立公園]]。<ref>{{cite web|title=Setonaikai National Park - Map 1|url=http://www.env.go.jp/park/setonaikai/intro/files/area_1.pdf|accessdate=2012-02-01|publisher=[[環境省|環境省]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130514171628/http://www.env.go.jp/park/setonaikai/intro/files/area_1.pdf|archive-date=2013-05-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>

